text: Hampus Eriksson (born September 11, 1996) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Brynäs IF of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Eriksson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Brynäs IF during the 2014–15 SHL season.http://www.brynas.se/artikel/64808/ ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Brynäs IF players Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards
